{"tid":246173,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[奇遇] 行行下街無啦啦走埋黎同我講","createTime":"2017-05-16T20:02:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T20:17:18.000Z","uid":77544,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6ca12a85557979d61006f30afc4148c4a6256a7c","tid":246173,"uid":77544,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T20:02:45.000Z","msg":"今日下晝一條友行過西洋菜街<br />\n行行下有個有陣過期MK味散發出黎既毒撚<br />\n奇奇怪怪咁樣行到去我面前<br />\n話想同我做個朋友<br />\n咁岩經過覺得我好特別<br />\n跟住我就有十萬個猜測<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一係PRANK緊一係做訪問一係想呃鳩我錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事關本人相貌真係柒柒地<br />\n<br />\n佢問我拎電話number<br />\n我就鳩俾左一個號碼佢<br />\n屌我一望<br />\n佢拎左部NOKIA彩MON推機出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經好撚奇怪<br />\n我O撚左咀望住佢<br />\n<br />\n重點黎啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 過期MK毒撚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無啦啦問我(好尷尬咁): 你交左租未?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (呆左): 下? 交咩租?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (依然好尷尬咁): 你已經係我心入面住左1分鐘, 你要交租俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住佢就走左<br />\n究竟佢想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 女<br />\n借fd ac 開post"},{"pid":"84aced4c00a9bbe0f86d51ed2c3d399027d8e1cb","tid":246173,"uid":43308,