":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:24:09.000Z","msg":"原來你咁睇我&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n斷你電煤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a1abcebe030884ed86a5aeaa813db69d2b3964d","tid":246173,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:37:48.000Z","msg":"鬼佬version<br />\n<br />\n今日下晝一條友行過西洋菜街<br />\n行行下有個有陣佬味既型棍鬼佬<br />\n斯斯文文咁樣行到去我面前<br />\n話想同我做個朋友<br />\n咁岩經過覺得我好特別<br />\n跟住我就有十萬個猜測<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通係上天注定既緣份？ 通勝講中左我今日行桃花運？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本人相貌真係吸引到鬼佬都唔奇<br />\n<br />\n佢問我拎電話number<br />\n我就俾晒有電話號碼佢<br />\n我一望<br />\n佢拎左部NOKIA彩MON推機出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚有個人style <br />\n我含情脈脈咁望住佢<br />\n<br />\n重點黎啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 型棍鬼佬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無啦啦問我(好尷尬咁): 你交左租未?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (呆左): 下? 交咩租?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (依然好尷尬咁): 你已經係我心入面住左1分鐘, 你要交租俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 濕晒喇衰鬼 鬼佬咁鬼浪漫<br />\n<br />\n跟住佢就走左<br />\n究竟佢想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}